<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Leicester East MP Claudia Webbe</p>

<p>Leicester East MP Claudia Webbe has been charged with an offence of harassment against one female, the Crown Prosecution Service said today.</p>

<p>In a statement, Jenny Hopkins of the CPS said: 'The CPS has today decided that Claudia Webbe, MP for Leicester East, should be charged with an offence of harassment against one female.</p>

<p>'The CPS made the decision after receiving a file of evidence from the Metropolitan Police.</p>

<p>'Criminal proceedings against Ms Webbe are now active and she has the right to a fair trial. </p>

<p>'It is extremely important that there should be no reporting, commentary or sharing of information online which could in any way prejudice these proceedings.'</p>

<p>More to follow </p>

<p>Leicester East MP Claudia Webbe is pictured with former Labour leader Jeremy Corbyn</p>
